settings.description: Test some of your skills with the Tanooki Suit in this brief adventure up in the sky!
Even if this editor seems kinda robust, it's kinda fun trying to build levels under the GBA's limitation. Level's mostly focused on the Triangular Block's mechanics.
Mario Falls down after taking on the airship he was on, he finds himself in this area, he will need to be careful and not die! Cloud Tower is next.
The 'Ultimate" airship is hare! You must board it and get through it, then fight Boom Boom, the airship creator! Don't die or you will be forced to restart, he is a lot harder this time!
Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...
